---
import { Star, MessageSquare, ExternalLink, Facebook } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="reviews-section section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="badge badge-gold">Opinie Klientów</span>
      <h2>Co mówią nasi klienci</h2>
      <p>Prawdziwe zdania od osób, u których ukończyliśmy prace glazurnicze i remontowe.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-wrapper">
      <div class="review-card glass-card">
        <div class="stars-row">
          {[...Array(5)].map((_, i) => (
            <Star key={i} size={18} class="star-icon fill-gold" />
          ))}
        </div>

        <blockquote class="review-quote">
          „Polecam. Porządna firma."
        </blockquote>

        <div class="review-author-row">
          <div class="author-avatar">SD</div>
          <div>
            <strong class="author-name">Szymon Dudek</strong>
            <span class="review-source">Opinia z Google · 5.0 / 5.0</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-invite-box">
      <MessageSquare size={20} class="text-gold" />
      <p>
        Dopiero zaczynamy zbierać opinie online — jeśli byliśmy u Ciebie, wystaw opinię na 
        <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=TSS+P%C5%82ytki+W%C5%82adys%C5%82aw+Kuchnia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="invite-link">
          <span>Google</span>
          <ExternalLink size={14} />
        </a>
        lub odwiedź nasz profil na 
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/tssplytki/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="invite-link">
          <span>Facebooku</span>
          <Facebook size={14} />
        </a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews-wrapper {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem auto;
  }

  .review-card {
    padding: 2.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .stars-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .star-icon.fill-gold {
    color: var(--accent-travertine);
    fill: var(--accent-travertine);
  }

  .review-quote {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .review-author-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-copper);
    color: #0D1117;
    font-weight: 800;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .author-name {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .review-source {
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .reviews-invite-box {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-stone);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.925rem;
  }

  .invite-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--accent-travertine);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .invite-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .reviews-invite-box {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
